      "value": "<div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have practiced techniques useful in melee combat against spellcasters, gaining the following benefits:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When a creature within 5 feet of you casts a spell, you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against that creature.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you damage a creature that is concentrating on a spell, that creature has disadvantage on the saving throw it makes to maintain its concentration.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on saving throws against spells cast by creatures within 5 feet of you.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t</div>",
